description:
The French documentary, called &amp;#039;The World According to Monsanto&amp;#039; and directed by independent filmmaker Marie-Monique Robin, paints a grim picture of a company with a long track record of environmental crimes and health scandals. Aired 03/11 on French television (ARTE - French-German cultural tv channel)

It&amp;#039;s all about &quot;better living through chemistry&quot;, and genetically modified food... if that&amp;#039;s what you want.

